Package: cbamm
Type: Package
Title: Collaborative Bayesian Adaptive Meta-Analysis Methods
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Mahmood", "Ahmad",
           email = "mahmood726@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a comprehensive framework for evidence synthesis through three
    primary innovations: (1) Population Transportability via entropy balancing
    weights, (2) Sequential Evidence Monitoring with Trial Sequential Analysis (TSA)
    boundaries, and (3) Automated decision support via a multi-persona synthesis
    engine. Includes fast Bayesian random-effects models with Bayes Factors (BF10)
    for hypothesis testing and evidence strength assessment.
